				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This may be a bit off the wall; however...
<br />

<br />
Having played a beastlord, I have had a lot of practice tanking for my pet and am wondering at what level it is no longer viable for magicians. The whole rationale for doing this is to get your melee skills up early on to lessen the pain of bringing them up at level 50 (or whatever).
<br />

<br />
I assume the best pet for this would be Air (for the stuns) and obviously fast weapons and good AC/HP and perhaps some extra Dex.
<br />

<br />
As a side question, is there an obvious best choice of weapon type or do we need to be proficient in all three?<br />_________________<br />Stromm server:
