			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It is all a matter of the situation.
<br />

<br />
Yes, at low levels as a magician you need to tank. The pet is paper.
<br />

<br />
When you get older you don't want to tank, because your tanking abilities are far below your pets and you can heal the pet not yourself. However, allowing yourself to take a hit or two will get your defence skills up, which will help in the long run. There are also the times where you can allow yourself to get hit if you are out of mana and it will make you win the fight.
<br />

<br />
Also, while it definitely isn't a thing you will do often, it is desirable to max at least one of the melee skills so you can bonk that pesky green skelly that aggroed.
<br />

<br />
nmee<br />_________________<br /><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=407265">Nmee Lightarch</A>
<br />
Prestidigitator
<br />
<A href="http://www.povartarewalliance.org/">Povar Tarew Alliance</A></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
