			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I had this problem some time ago, as my DEF skill, in my eyes our most important combatskill, was at a meager 30. I found it very hard to increase it, as any mob that was viable to give me a skill up would also give me quite a pounding.
<br />

<br />
I therefore suggest that you get a nice hp buff, and move to Echo Caverns, on the FG side. The Needlites there are the quickest creatures I know off, with a delay of a mere 10 i.e. 1 sec. They only double, and do not even hit very hard. If you want to play it even safer, put up a DS, chances are the Needlite will kill itself on the DS before it is able to kill you.
<br />

<br />
I suggest this camp also for all other classes, and it works nicely to train Riposte too  <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="razz" border="0" /> .</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
